00:00:32.590 --> 00:00:36.829
and a vaccination was created in the late
50s; the measles has been a relatively easy

00:00:36.829 --> 00:00:38.039
disease to control.

00:00:38.039 --> 00:00:45.120
In fact, our regional strain of the measles
was eliminated from the US as of 2000, but

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:48.789
it's still fairly common in Europe, Asia,
Africa and the Pacific.

00:00:48.789 --> 00:00:53.210
