long people.

00:01:04.890 --> 00:01:12.229
2015 has already had 59 cases, from a single
Disneyland exposure -- including five employees

00:01:12.229 --> 00:01:13.280
of the parks.

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:15.039
The measles is REALLY contagious.

00:01:15.039 --> 00:01:19.140
It was first described in some way by Persian
physicians in the year 900.

00:01:19.140 --> 00:01:24.399
It causes a rash all over your body, swelling,
fever, a cough and little spots inside the

00:01:24.399 --> 00:01:26.420
cheeks called Koplik spots.

00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:30.820
It's deadly to young children and is one of
the leading causes for children worldwide.

00:01:30.820 --> 00:01:34.560
Measles, or rubeola is a virus, and there
is no cure.

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:39.189
It spreads by flying into the air during a
cough or sneeze or piggybacking on the sharing

00:01:39.189 --> 00:01:40.189
of food or drinks.

00:01:40.189 --> 00:01:42.790
If you had the measles and you're watching
this, CONGRATULATIONS!

00:01:42.790 --> 00:01:45.729
Tell us about history Nana and PopPop!!

00:01:45.729 --> 00:01:50.369
Most people born before 1957 have had the
measles; so I just want to make them feel

00:01:50.369 --> 00:01:51.369
included.

00:01:51.369 --> 00:01:56.859
The reason the cutoff is 1957 -- is because
in 1958** a vaccine went into wide use and

00:01:56.859 --> 00:01:57.859
boom.

00:01:57.859 --> 00:02:00.439
Measles infections dropped precipitously.

00:02:00.439 --> 00:02:05.130
Since then, the WHO has attempted to vaccinate
children worldwide, which likely saved hundreds

00:02:05.130 --> 00:02:06.609
of thousands of lives.

00:02:06.609 --> 00:02:12.050
Since 2000 they've dropped cases 75% worldwide
thanks to the MMR vaccine.

00:02:12.050 --> 00:02:16.780
The vaccine for the measles is part of the
MMR vaccine; which stands for measles-mumps

00:02:16.780 --> 00:02:17.780
and rubella.

00:02:17.780 --> 00:02:21.440
Measles is the worst, but the mumps causes
a swelling of the parotid glands giving the

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:25.110
face a hamster look; sounds cute, but it's
not cute.

00:02:25.110 --> 00:02:26.760
It's painful and highly contagious.

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:32.270
It can also caught inflammation of the testis,
ovary, pancreas, or meninges.

00:02:32.270 --> 00:02:38.050
Rubella is also known as the german measles,
and it's like the measles, but far milder.

00:02:38.050 --> 00:02:41.350
Luckily, the MMR vaccine is one of the most
effective in the world.

00:02:41.350 --> 00:02:46.400
With only two doses, 97-percent of human immune
systems create enough antibodies to fight

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:48.290
off any measles it may come in contact with.

00:02:48.290 --> 00:02:51.930
Usually, the first comes near birth, and the
second a few years later to make sure the

00:02:51.930 --> 00:02:54.100
immunity is solid.

00:02:54.100 --> 00:02:58.330
Measles sounds crappy, what with the rashes
and diarrhea, but it can also cause permanent

00:02:58.330 --> 00:02:59.740
damage to the lungs or the brain.

00:02:59.740 --> 00:03:03.980
It's also connected to seizures and meningitis!

